      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:28] (expert) to quickly toss a cloth over the head or dispel magic (5th level; counteract DC 28) against the statue to suppress the magic for [[/br 1d4 #minutes]]{1d4 minutes}. Worshippers of Zon-Kuthon are immune to all effects of the Statue of Kazavon.</p>",
